data.description: Welcome to 9219 Lakeshores Lagoon Lane. This stunning real estate gem offers a luxurious living experience with exquisite features and unparalleled craftsmanship. With a thoughtful design and meticulous attention to detail, this home is sure to captivate your senses. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of high ceilings that create an open and spacious atmosphere throughout the house. Prepare to be impressed by the balconies that overlook the entry and living areas, providing a unique vantage point and adding a touch of architectural charm. The dual master closets are a standout feature, offering an abundance of storage space and ensuring that organization is a breeze. The study, adorned with glass French doors, provides a perfect space for productivity and focus. Beautiful wood floors add warmth and sophistication. This property is a serene retreat from the hustle and bustle of the city while still being conveniently close to shopping, amenities and entertainment.
